oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Elmer Fudpucker's Billy Deaton Talent featuring Faron Young (undated)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Fudpucker, Elmer; Young, Faron; Houston, David, 1937-; Howard, Jan (Vocalist); Phillips, Stu; Smith, Connie, 1941-;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing a Billy Deaton Talent with Faron Young and the Deputies, David Houston and the Persuaders, Jan Howard, Stu Phillips, Connie Smith, Del Wood, Phyllis Day, DeWayne Orinder, and Robin Young. Poster is undated and features metal photoplates of Faron Young, David Houston, Jan Howard, Stu Phillips, and Connie Smith.
